parameters:
Bunny-chan: Alright, tonight marks the start of Monster
Fight!! It's the third showdown between Cerberus Octopus-
sama and Shark Duke-sama! Will we see a comeback home run
tonight?!

Spectator: Just lose already, Shark Duke!! I started saving
up just to have sex with you!! Don't you dare win until I've
saved up 250,000!!

Spectator: Fighting with your pussy fully exposed, huh?! You
lewd Duke!! A woman who's sucked off every man in the city
is something else!! If you lose next time, you better just
go about naked!!

Memimi: I-I haven't... sucked off everyone... damn it, damn
it...!

Cerberus Octopus: Kekeke... you never learn, do you? Your
position gets worse every time you lose! This time for sure,
I'll engrain defeat into your heart so you'll never defy me
again, I'll shred you to bits!!

Bunny-chan: Okaaay, 10 seconds to start~. Please get to your
starting positions~❤️ Good luck to both of you~❤️

Memimi: Gah... what is this... the weight of these
punches... They're on par with the giant-type monsters...
And there's speed too... it's... too strong...!

Cerberus Octopus: Kekeke, it's all in vain... No monster can
slip through my Octopus Arms! A lightly armored wretch like
you is easy prey!!
Memimi: It doesn't hurt at all...

Cerberus Octopus: Wh-what...? My Cerberus Blow didn't go
off... Ahh!?

Cerberus Octopus: My Octopus Arms are damaged...!! They
couldn't withstand the weight at the tip... what a
disaster...

Memimi: A malfunction with the monster suit... This is my
chance!! Here I go!!!

Cerberus Octopus: UGYAAAA-----!!! To think such a thing
could happen... foolish... I underestimated Shark Duke...
collapses...

Bunny-chan: It's a grand! Comeback! Victory for Shark Duke-
sama❤️ Congratulations, a successful revenge~♪

Memimi: That was close... Thank goodness... I-I won... Phew,
that was scary...

Memimi's organization absorbed and merged with Cerberus
Octopus's organization, becoming one of the largest super
organizations in the city...
